sentences.sentence: "I bet most never touch the ground in their 20 to 30 years of life," says Kays.
sentences.translation: “我敢打赌，这些可以活上二三十年的小动物们也许一辈子都不曾接触过地面，”凯斯说。

sentences.sentence: "Lions don't care if it's raining or not raining. They care about what native prey is available," Kays said.
sentences.translation: 对此，罗兰·凯解释到：“狮子并不在乎是下雨还是不下雨，它们关心的是食物。”
